#intro role="banner"
	.final-edition-intro
		h1 The End 
		img src="/assets/images/content/blend-conference-logo.png" alt="Blend Conference"
		h2 in Charlotte, NC

		p Blend Conference had a good run and was hosted in the glorious city of Charlotte. For 3 days you could shut your devices off and enjoy some lovely conversations about user experience, design, and&nbsp;development and our fabulous speakers. For posterity, we present you a wrap-up of each year.
	.button-group
		a.primary-button href="http://2013.blendconf.com" 2013
		a.primary-button href="http://2014.blendconf.com" 2014
		a.primary-button href="http://2015.blendconf.com" 2015

#skinny
	h2: span Something Different
	ul
		li 
			svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24": use xlink:href="#no-devices-icon"
			strong No Devices
			| Wait. What? You read that right. Every year we ripped folks apart from the technology they loved so much. Laptops, tablets and phones weren't allowed during our conference&nbsp;sessions.
		li 
			svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24": use xlink:href="#notebook-icon"
			strong Custom Notebooks
			| We went analog. Each person received a custom hard cover notebook along with something fancy to write with. They took notes, doodled some sketch notes, or jotted down the names of new&nbsp;friends.
		li 
			svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24": use xlink:href="#diversity-icon"
			strong Diversity
			| Every year we spent months curating a diverse group of talented speakers. Some spoke often. Others spoke for the first time. We also did out best to help attract a diverse group of fellow&nbsp;attendees. 

#speakers
	h2: span Our Alumni
	p Over the 3 years of the conference we invited over 160 different folks in our industry come to Charlotte. They were amazing, kind, and did such a great job making BlendConf what it was.

	h3 Keynotes
	ul.keynote-speakers
		- data.speakers.sort_by {|s| s.lastName}.each do |speaker|
			- if speaker.type == "Keynotes"
				li class="#{clean_data(speaker.firstName)}-#{clean_data(speaker.lastName)}"
					/ a href="/speakers/#{clean_data(speaker.firstName)}-#{clean_data(speaker.lastName)}/"
					a href="#"
						strong.speaker-name #{speaker.firstName} #{speaker.lastName} <span>#{speaker.company}</span>
						strong.speaker-talk-title #{speaker.talkTitle} <span>#{speaker.discipline}</span>
						img src="/assets/images/content/speakers/#{clean_data(speaker.firstName)}-#{clean_data(speaker.lastName)}.jpg"

	h3 Sessions
	ul.session-speakers
		- data.speakers.sort_by {|s| s.lastName}.each do |speaker|
